@section Tutorial part 3: Loops and variables


Consider this C function:

@quotation

@example
int loop_test (int n)
@{
  int sum = 0;
  for (int i = 0; i < n; i++)
    sum += i * i;
  return sum;
@}
@end example

@noindent
@end quotation

